            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Rough example with components mode, filename, diagnostics, filetype, line:col, %file:\r\n\r\n```lua\r\nvim.o.statusline = '  %{luaeval(\"Mode()\")} │ %f%m %=│ %{luaeval(\"Dia()\")}│ %{&filetype} │ %l:%c │ %03(%p%)%%  '\r\n```\r\n\r\n<img width=\"713\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/23235841/a4b21178-e228-41d2-90c4-ee6ec7c9b111\">\r\n\r\nNot sure if lua components can be made/used, and if so, how to do that without luaeval.\r\n",
